  "design_notes": "Hard chart designed to match the 173.3 BPM tempo. Standard 8th-note streams are used for the main drops to keep the NPS comfortably around 5.8, well below the 8.0 limit. Sparser step patterns in the intro and build track the lower energy. Holds are precisely paced to hit 8.6% of the chart density, well within the 5-12% budget. Grids are used at the very end to ensure there are no dead pauses during the final silent outro.",
